explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the role of stock and interbank markets in measuring bank performance in East Asian countries, employing panel regression techniques. It does not mention or involve any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models, nor does it discuss any related concepts such as supervised learning, unsupervised learning, neural networks, or any other keywords from the provided list. The study is purely econometric and financial in nature, analyzing market responses to bank risk and performance without the use of advanced computational or AI-based methods.
